INSERT INTO `file_data` VALUES (1,3,5,'about_us','\"When a campus full of a myriad of people and ideas reaches a critical mass, the latent energy awakens to manifest itself into a grandeur.\\r\\nFelicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT Hyderabad.\\r\\nThe students of the institute come together to create an event that is the expression of their creativity and technical prowess.\\r\\nCome experience a zestful three day long bonanza that has something for everyone!\"'),(2,5,8,'title','\"Schedule\"'),(3,10,14,'name','\"Threads\"'),(4,10,14,'tagline','\"Think. Solve. Code.\"'),(5,10,14,'short_description','\"The tech contest\"'),(6,10,14,'long_description','\"Felicity team brings to you Threads \'15, the annual coding extravaganza, organized by IIIT Hyderabad. Spread across seven weeks we present challenges from varied fields of programming and computer systems. Brace yourself for a new challenge every weekend showing you different aspect of the computing world. Though BEWARE, sometimes you need more than computing to find the treasure.\"'),(7,10,14,'nav_icon','\"icon-code\"'),(8,12,17,'name','\"Pulsation\"'),(9,12,17,'tagline','\"Innovate. Design. Automate.\"'),(10,12,17,'short_description','\"Electronics events\"'),(11,12,17,'long_description','\" What is the digital age without digital electronics? For those who\'s heart is but an IC that pumps bits instead of blood, pulsation is here to resonate with the frequency of your hearts!\"'),(12,12,18,'nav_icon','\"icon-doc\"'),(13,14,21,'name','\"Litcafe\"'),(14,14,21,'tagline','\"If word play is your fore play. Be there!\"'),(15,14,21,'short_description','\"The literary contest\"'),(16,14,21,'long_description','\"In cities full of large malls and big restaurants and in a society where the paradigm of large reigns our imagination, sometimes that small little caf\\u00e9 in one corner of the road with just 4 tables catches my attention. It is that small cozy place which is frequented by a small group of people. The owner knows everyone and there is a comfortable sense of belonging to that place which serves as a retreat from everything big and extravagant. Do you relate to that kind of a place? Well LitCafe at Felicity is exactly that kind of a place. In a fest that is alive with a myriad events, a small group of people gather to stimulate their creative centers and have a good time. From creative writing to speaking, there are events to suit everyone\\u2019s tastes.\"'),(17,14,21,'nav_icon','\"icon-pencil\"'),(18,10,22,'long_description','\"Felicity team brings to you Threads \\u02bc16, the annual coding extravaganza, organized by IIIT Hyderabad. Spread across seven weeks we present challenges from varied fields of programming and computer systems. Brace yourself for a new challenge every weekend showing you different aspect of the computing world. Though BEWARE, sometimes you need more than computing to find the treasure.\"'),(19,15,24,'name','\"CodeCraft\"'),(20,15,24,'tagline','\"So, you think you can code?\"'),(21,15,24,'description','\"The annual grand algorithmic sprint is back yet again, based on ACM ICPC format.\"'),(22,15,24,'start_time','\"2016-01-31 14:00\"'),(23,15,24,'end_time','\"2016-01-31 19:00\"'),(24,15,25,'contact_email','\"threads@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(25,16,27,'name','\"Gordian Knot\"'),(26,16,27,'tagline','\"The Project Euler of Felicity\"'),(27,16,27,'description','\"For the real world counterparts of Charlie Eppes, of Numb3rs, the annual Project Euler-styled mathematical contest is back as the paradise for lovers of mathematics and computing.\"'),(28,16,27,'start_time','\"2016-01-10 00:00\"'),(29,16,27,'end_time','\"2016-01-11 00:00\"'),(30,16,27,'contact_email','\"threads@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(31,17,29,'name','\"Break In CTF\"'),(32,17,29,'tagline','\"Break & Get In\"'),(33,17,29,'description','\"The official Capture The Flag event for Felicity Threads. Break In is a jeopardy-style CTF event, where you use whatever means at your disposal to win. If you enjoy finding ways in which a system can be broken, this event is for you.\"'),(34,17,29,'start_time','\"2016-01-24 00:00\"'),(35,17,29,'end_time','\"2016-01-26 00:00\"'),(36,17,29,'contact_email','\"threads@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(37,18,31,'name','\"Cache In\"'),(38,18,31,'tagline','\"Better you think -> Better you find\"'),(39,18,31,'description','\"Do puzzles and riddles excite you? Can you form one cohesive thought out of discrete ideas? Do you have a blend of Langdon, Jones and Holmes inside you? \\r\\n\\r\\nIf the answer to the above questions is a resounding \'yes\', we have brought \\\"Cache-in\\\" to whet your appetite.\\r\\nPlay with images, URLs and your brain until you unlock a mystery, but only to find a tougher one ahead.\"'),(40,18,31,'start_time','\"2016-01-14 00:00\"'),(41,18,31,'end_time','\"2016-01-15 00:00\"'),(42,18,31,'contact_email','\"threads@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(43,19,33,'name','\"Kings of ML\"'),(44,19,33,'tagline','\"Do not regret, just regress\"'),(45,19,33,'description','\"Do not make the mistake of considering this as just another coding contest. Each question here is an exotic research problem in itself. So gear up all your statistics, machine learning, data mining and most importantly your intuition.\"'),(46,19,33,'start_time','\"2016-02-09 00:00\"'),(47,19,33,'end_time','\"2016-02-14 00:00\"'),(48,19,33,'contact_email','\"threads@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(49,20,35,'name','\"TLE\"'),(50,20,35,'tagline','\"Dare to code beyond the norms\"'),(51,20,35,'description','\"The coding contest that pushes you beyond your comfort zones. From esoteric programming to obfuscation, it welcomes any dirty tricks you can play with the code.\\r\\n\\r\\nA 24 hr long programming contest with a twist.\\r\\nA coding contest full with unnatural programming challenges that would require smart solutions and tricks.\\r\\n\\r\\nPrimary language is going to be C, but knowledge of other languages, and love for esoteric and obfuscated programming would make your life easier.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe Contest will require you to not only solve the problem, but try solving them within some constraints on time, space and code.\"'),(52,20,35,'start_time','\"2016-01-17 00:00\"'),(53,20,35,'end_time','\"2016-01-18 00:00\"'),(54,20,35,'contact_email','\"threads@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(55,21,37,'name','\"Kernel Cruise\"'),(56,21,37,'tagline','\"Harness those clock cycles!\"'),(57,21,37,'description','\"Felicity Threads \\u02bc16 presents to you Kernel Cruise, a platform where you\\u2019ll be pitched against various computational problems, varying from combinatorial to numerical in nature, on a General Purpose GPU computing environment.\\r\\nGPUs are data parallel machines, with a multitude of processors on single chip capable of performing similar computations over chunks of a large amount of data, and involves vector processing. They are programmed using frameworks such CUDA, which is available for Nvidia GPU machines.\\r\\n\\r\\nProgramming parallel machines involves much greater skill than programming single core machines, as vectorization, synchronization, and distribution come up as major challenges. And it is this dragon of parallelism, that we invite you to battle.\\r\\n\\r\\nAnd if you haven\'t faced this dragon before, don\'t worry, as we\'ll be having familiarization phase for one week before the contest, wherein you\'ll be given access to machines, in addition to problems and tutorials, for learning and practice.\"'),(58,21,37,'start_time','\"2016-01-18 00:00\"'),(59,21,37,'end_time','\"2016-01-24 00:00\"'),(60,21,37,'contact_email','\"threads@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(61,22,39,'name','\"Botomata\"'),(62,22,39,'tagline','\"May the best bot win\"'),(63,22,39,'description','\"Botomata belongs to a new genre of AI and combinatorial search contests, and will contain challenges from puzzles like Sudoku, Kakuro, Rubik\'s Cube, and games like Reversi, for you to play with and devise effective search strategies and heuristics f