ans to collect your personal information (Which means information about an individual which can identify the specific individual, like name, date of birth, nationality, location, gender, email address, phone numbers, organisations, etc. ) to the extent necessary to achieve the purpose for use prescribed in this Privacy Policy. We do not collect information regarding your race, ancestry, lineage, religion, political views or membership of workers\\u2019 unions.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>For any given individual\\u2019s personal information we collect, we consider Name and Contact Details like email address and phone number to be Sensitive Information, and the rest to be Safe-To-Aggregate Data.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Sharing of Information<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Public Sharing<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nOf the information collected for each individual, Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad will publicly share nicknames\\/usernames, country and college\\/organisation details of each individual. Your name may be disclosed publicly under some circumstances.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Disclosure to Third Parties<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Of the information collected for each individual, Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad will disclose only Safe-To-Aggregate Data of each individual to third parties (such as sponsors). None of the information classified as Sensitive Information will be disclosed to third parties, aside from your email id, which may be disclosed to sponsors when we deem necessary.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Children<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We will not knowingly collect Personal Information via the Sites from visitors younger than thirteen (13) years of age. We treat all our customers as adults in the wake of this declaration,  however, and we strongly encourage parents to talk to their children about their use of the Internet and the information they disclose on websites.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Cookies and Google Analytics<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>A cookie is a piece of text placed on your computer by a web server. We occasionally use coo