tates without stepping on a bomb. To achieve this you can perform 3 types of actions.\",\"M X: Move to cell X with respect to your position. X is 2 for Left, 4 for Down, 6 for Right, 8 for Up.<br>Action Cost: 1.<br>You win if you reach a goal state and the game ends.<br>You lose if you reach a bomb and the game ends.\",\"SC: Ask for the number of bombs in the 5x5 grid centered at your position.<br>Action Cost: 1<br>The system replies with the number of bombs in the mentioned grid.\",\"SE X: Ask for the \\u2018heuristic\\u2019 value at cell \\u2018X\\u2019. Possible values of X  are {1-9} where 1 is the top left corner and number increase in anti-clockwise direction.<br>The Heuristic values is defined as the sum of Euclidean distances of all goals from the position X.<br>Action Cost: 2<br>System replies with heuristic values if it is a free cell.<br>System reply is -1 if the position is a bomb.\"]'),(636,22,477,'status','\"Contest begins in a few minutes!\"'),(637,22,478,'rules','[\"You are placed inside a grid with multiple goals and bombs. You aim to reach ANY of the goal states without stepping on a bomb. To achieve this you can perform 3 types of actions.\",\"M X: Move to cell X with respect to your position. X is 2 for Left, 4 for Down, 6 for Right, 8 for Up.<br>Action Cost: 1.<br>You win if you reach a goal state and the game ends.<br>You lose if you reach a bomb and the game ends.\",\"SC: Ask for the number of bombs in the 5x5 grid centered at your position.<br>Action Cost: 1<br>The system replies with the number of bombs in the mentioned grid.\",\"SE X: Ask for the \\u2018heuristic\\u2019 value at cell \\u2018X\\u2019. Possible values of X  are {1-9} where 1 is the top left corner and number increase in anti-clockwise direction.<br>The Heuristic values is defined as the sum of Euclidean distances of all goals from the position X.<br>Action Cost: 2<br>System replies with heuristic values if it is a free cell.<br>System reply is \'B\' if the position is a bomb.\"]'),(638,22,479,'rules','[\"You are placed inside a grid with multiple goals and bombs. You aim to reach ANY of the goal states without stepping on a bomb. To achieve this you can perform 3 types of actions.\",\"M X: Move to cell X with respect to your position. X is 2 for Left, 4 for Down, 6 for Right, 8 for Up.<br>Action Cost: 1.<br>You win if you reach a goal state and the game ends.<br>You lose if you reach a bomb and the game ends.\",\"SC: Ask for the number of bombs in the 5x5 grid centered at your position.<br>Action Cost: 1<br>The system replies with the number of bombs in the mentioned grid.\",\"SE X: Ask for the \\u2018heuristic\\u2019 value at cell \\u2018X\\u2019. Possible values of X  are {1-9} where 1 is the top left corner and number increase in anti-clockwise direction.<br>The Heuristic values is defined as the sum of Euclidean distances of all goals from the position X.<br>Action Cost: 2<br>System replies with heuristic values if it is a free cell.<br>System replies with \'G\' in case of goal state.<br>System reply is \'B\' if the position has a bomb.\"]'),(639,31,481,'button_link','\"contest\\/litquiz\\/\"'),(640,31,481,'button_text','\"Contest Started\"'),(641,22,482,'status','\"Contest is now Live!\"'),(642,22,482,'button_link','\"contest\\/botomata\\/\"'),(643,22,482,'button_text','\"Link To Contest\"'),(644,22,483,'end_time','\"2016-02-15 12:00\"'),(645,22,484,'rules','[\"Your bot is not allowed to do any form of Network I\\/O or disk I\\/O. \",\"Attempts made to attack \\/ break the system will be disqualified.\",\"Use of non builtin libraries is not allowed.\",\"Winners will be announced post contest after a manual evaluation of submissions.\"]'),(646,57,485,'tagline','\"Joga Bonito\"'),(647,57,485,'description','\" 4-a-side Futsal is coming to Felicity!\"'),(648,57,485,'button_link','\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/sports\\/futsal\\/register\\/\"'),(649,57,486,'start_time','\"2016-02-19 11:00\"'),(650,57,486,'end_time','\"2016-02-20 17