ND THE PERFECT DESIGNATION FOR YOUR PROPOSED CELEBRATION--A TIME OF ENJOYMENT, REVELLING, APPRECIATION OF THE PRIVILEGE, FREEDOM AND COMFORT GIVEN TO YOU, SENSE OF CELEBRATION, THE FEELING AND HOPE (IF NOT CONVICTION) THAT \\\"EVERYTHING-IS-ALRIGHT-WITH-THE-WORLD\\\"\\r\\nFelicity.\\r\\n -Someone we know.\\r\\n\\r\\nA year\'s worth of excitement, fervor, and hard work packed into 3 amazing days. \\r\\nFelicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT-Hyderabad, and would go on from January 27th, to 29th. This time, our theme celebrates that one merry period of life, when we were young, curious, and free. This Felicity we dedicate these three days to walk you through your childhood once again, and take a dip in the nostalgia of the 90s. \\r\\nFelicity \'17, Remembering our Childhood.\\\"\"'),(861,3,641,'about_us','\"When a campus full of a myriad of people and ideas reaches a critical mass, the latent energy awakens to manifest itself into a grandeur. Felicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT Hyderabad. The students of the institute come together to create an event that is the expression of their creativity and technical prowess. Come experience a zestful three day long bonanza that has something for everyone!\\r\\n\"'),(862,3,643,'about_us','\"<h1>When a campus full of a myriad of people and ideas reaches a critical mass, the latent energy awakens to manifest itself into a grandeur. Felicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT Hyderabad. The students of the institute come together to create an event that is the expression of their creativity and technical prowess. Come experience a zestful three day long bonanza that has something for everyone!<\\/h1>\\r\\n\"'),(863,3,644,'about_us','\"When a campus full of a myriad of people and ideas reaches a critical mass, the latent energy awakens to manifest itself into a grandeur. Felicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT Hyderabad. The students of the institute come together to create an event that is the expression of their creativity and technical prowess. Come experience a zestful three day long bonanza that has something for everyone!\\r\\n\"'),(864,3,645,'about_us','\"<blockquote><p class=\\\"page about-content\\\"><i>I believe I have found the perfect designation for the proposed celebration - A time of enjoyment, revelling, appreciation of the privilege, freedom and comfort given to you, a sense of celebration, the feeling and hope that everything is alright with the world - Felicity.<\\/i><\\/p><\\/blockquote>\\r\\n<br\\/><br\\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"page about-content\\\">A year\'s worth of excitement, fervour and hard work packed into 3 amazing days. \\r\\nFelicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT-Hyderabad, and would go on from January 27th to 29th. This time, our theme celebrates that one merry period of life, when we were young, curious and free. This Felicity we dedicate these three days to walk you through your childhood once again, and take a dip in the nostalgia of the 90\'s. <br\\/>\\r\\nFelicity \'17 - Forever Young.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"'),(865,50,647,'body','\"<p>\\r\\nThis Privacy Policy is designed to tell you about the practices regarding collection, use, and disclosure of information that may be collected by Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad. Please be sure to read this entire Privacy Policy, before using or submitting information to the websites owned or operated by Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Consent<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>By using the sites or services provided by Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad, you agree to the Terms of this Privacy Policy. Whenever you submit information to Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of that information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Information<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>At Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad, we use fair and proper means to collect your personal information (Which means information about an individual which can identify the specific individual, like name, date of birth, nationality, location, gender, email address, phone numbers, organisations, etc. ) to the extent necessary to achieve the purpose for use prescribed in this Privacy Policy. We do not collect information regarding your race, ancestry, lineage, religion, political views or membership of workers\\u2019 unions.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>For any given individual\\u2019s personal information we collect, we consider Name and Contact Details like email address and phone number to be Sensitive Information, and the rest to be Safe-To-Aggregate Data.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Sharing of Information<\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Public Sharing<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>\\r\\nOf the information collected for each individual, Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad will publicly share nicknames\\/usernames, country and college\\/organisation details of each individual. Your name may be disclosed publicly under some circumstances.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Disclosure to Third Parties<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>Of the information collected for each individual, Felicity, IIIT-Hyderabad will disclose only Safe-To-Aggregate Data of each individual to third parties (such as sponsors). None of the information classified as Sensitive Information will be disclosed to third parties, aside from your email id, which may be disclosed to sponsors when we deem necessary.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Children<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>We will not knowingly collect Personal Information via the Sites from visitors younger than thirteen (13) years of age. We treat all our customers as adults in the wake of this declaration,  however, and we strongly encourage parents to talk to their children about their use of the Internet and the information they disclose on websites.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h2>Cookies and Google Analytics<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>A cookie is a piece of text placed on your computer by a web server. We occasionally use cookies on some parts of our web services to enhance your experience of the site. We may use a session cookie to store a randomly generated identifying tag on your computer. Session cookies are temporary and are automatically deleted during operation of your browser or when your browser is closed.\\r\\nMost web browsers may be customized to refuse new cookies or delete existing cookies. Rejecting or deleting cookies may limit your ability to take advantage of some of our features and could result in the loss of any customized setting.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>We also use Google Analytics to analyze traffic to our website and its services. Data generated through Google Analytics can be linked, by the Google Analytics customer or by Google, using Google technology, to third-party cookies, related to visits to other websites.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><em><small>This privacy policy was last updated on the 16th of December, 2017.<\\/small><\\/em><\\/p>\"'),(866,3,649,'about_us','\"<blockquote><p class=\\\"page about-content\\\"><i>I believe I have found the perfect designation for the proposed celebration - A time of enjoyment, revelling, appreciation of the privilege, freedom and comfort given to you, a sense of celebration, the feeling and hope that everything is alright with the world - Felicity<\\/i><\\/p><\\/blockquote>\\r\\n<br\\/><br\\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"page about-content\\\">A year\'s worth of excitement, fervour and hard work packed into 3 amazing days. \\r\\nFelicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT-Hyderabad, and would go on from January 27th to 29th. This time, our theme celebrates that one merry period of life, when we were young, curious and free. This Felicity we dedicate these three days to walk you through your childhood once again, and take a dip in the nostalgia of the 90\'s. <br\\/>\\r\\nFelicity \'17 - Forever Young.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"'),(867,3,650,'about_us','\"<blockquote><p class=\\\"page about-content\\\"><i>I believe I have found the perfect designation for the proposed celebration - A time of enjoyment, revelling, appreciation of the privilege, freedom and comfort given to you, a sense of celebration, the feeling and hope that everything is alright with the world - Felicity.<\\/i><\\/p><\\/blockquote>\\r\\n<br\\/><br\\/>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p class=\\\"page about-content\\\">A year\'s worth of excitement, fervour and hard work packed into 3 amazing days. \\r\\nFelicity is the annual techno-cultural fest of IIIT-Hyderabad, and would go on from January 27th to 29th. This time, our theme celebrates that one merry period of life, when we were young, curious and free. This Felicity we dedicate these three days to walk you through your childhood once again, and take a dip in the nostalgia of the 90\'s. <br\\/>\\r\\nFelicity \'17 - Forever Young.<\\/p>\\r\\n\"'),(868,18,651,'start_time','\"2017-01-06 00:00\"'),(869,18,651,'end_time','\"2017-01-07 00:00\"'),(870,18,652,'description','\"Here are the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/files\\/16\\/cachein-explanations.pdf\\\" class=\\\"underlined\\\">explanations for all the questions.<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nDo puzzles and riddles excite you Can you form one cohesive thought out of discrete ideas? Do you have a blend of Langdon, Jones and Holmes inside you? \\r\\n\\r\\nIf the answer to the above questions is a resounding \'yes\', we have brought \\\"Cache-in\\\" to whet your appetite.\\r\\nPlay with images, URLs and your brain until you unlock a mystery, but only to find a new one ahead.\"'),(871,18,653,'description','\"Here are the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/files\\/16\\/cachein-explanations.pdf\\\" class=\\\"underlined\\\">explanations for all the questions.<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nDo puzzles and riddles excite you? Can you form one cohesive thought out of discrete ideas? Do you have a blend of Langdon, Jones and Holmes inside you? \\r\\n\\r\\nIf the answer to the above questions is a resounding \'yes\', we have brought \\\"Cache-in\\\" to whet your appetite.\\r\\nPlay with images, URLs and your brain until you unlock a mystery, but only to find a new one ahead.\"'),(872,74,656,'about_us','\"Testing\"'),(873,74,661,'name','\"ssa\"'),(874,74,661,'tagline','\"asas\"'),(875,74,661,'description','\"asasas\"'),(876,49,664,'name','\"Counter Strike Global Offensive\"'),(877,49,664,'description','\"\\\"Follow me !\\\", \\\"Roger that.\\\" Do these words bring an adrenaline rush to your gaming senses. If it doesn\'t you are not living a life. \\r\\nIn case of Counter Strike, the thing is not who plays it, it is instead who does not.\\r\\nZombie Zone, Felicity 2017 brings before you, Counter-Strike:Global Offensive.\\r\\nSo get set, reach the Market Place, and buy everything you need from magnums to grenades! Because, only the best will win! \"'),(878,49,664,'rules','[\"Teams must have at least 5 players.\",\"Maps: VETO map system, Finals BO3, rest all rounds BO1.\",\"Standard hardware will be provided at the venue. However, teams can bring their own equipments\",\"Standard CS Clan rules apply. \",\"Players must enter their Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (SteamID) game ID\",\"Max Rounds: 30\",\"Standard Mappool:de_dust2     de_nuke     de_mirage     de_train     de_cache     de_cobblestone     de_overpass\"]'),(879,49,665,'rules','[\"Teams must have at least 5 players.\",\"Players must enter their Counter-Strike: Global Offensive (SteamID) game ID\",\"Maps: VETO map system, Finals BO3, rest all rounds BO1.\",\"Max Rounds: 30\",\"Standard Mappool:      de_dust2     de_nuke     de_mirage     de_train     de_cache     de_cobblestone     de_overpass\",\"Standard hardware will be provided at the venue. However, teams can bring their own equipments\",\"Standard CS Clan rules apply. \"]'),(880,49,665,'start_time','\"2017-01-27 09:30\"'),(881,49,665,'end_time','\"2017-01-29 18:30\"'),(882,74,667,'name','\"Visualize It\"'),(883,65,669,'name','\"Kode Da Ckt\"'),(884,65,669,'tagline','\"So you think you think you can code?  Ever tried coding a circuit?\"'),(885,65,669,'description','\"Do you have the best circuit designing skills? Or, are you are a starter and want to practice and compete against the best?\\r\\nCome join us to innovate with your designs and code your brains out this Felicity.\"'),(886,65,669,'rules','[\"You will have 10 problems and 36 hours.\",\"There is no partial scoring for any problem.\",\"This is an individual event. Any type of plagiarism will lead to disqualification.\",\"Users will be ranked first on the number of problems solved and then on the sum of time penalty for all accepted problems.\",\"Allowed Languages: VHDL,Verilog\"]'),(887,65,669,'start_time','\"2017-01-20 18:00\"'),(888,65,669,'end_time','\"2017-01-21 18:00\"'),(889,65,669,'venue','\"Online. Portal will be put up soon.\"'),(890,75,671,'name','\"Pulse Up\"'),(891,75,671,'tagline','\"The same old QuizUp, electronic avatar!\"'),(892,75,671,'description','\"QuizUp - the game which got us all addicted. This version of the game is sure to get you hooked up. \\r\\nJoin us in this pulse racing competition. \"'),(893,75,671,'rules','[\"You will have twenty seconds to answer each question.\",\"There will be ten questions.\",\"Time-based scoring including negative marking for any incorrect attempt.\",\"Three levels.\"]'),(894,75,671,'start_time','\"2017-01-15 08:00\"'),(895,75,671,'end_time','\"2017-01-15 23:45\"'),(896,75,671,'venue','\"Online. Portal will be put up soon.\"'),(897,75,671,'contact_email','\"pulsation@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(898,76,673,'name','\"Robo Soccer\"'),(899,76,673,'tagline','\"The Messis and Ronaldos of the robotics world\"'),(900,76,673,'description','\"Want to create the Messis and Ronaldos of the robotics world? This thrilling event is just for you. We will give you everything you need and teach you everything you need to know, you just need to come out and play. \\r\\n\\r\\nThe event consists of 2 parts.\\r\\nThe first two days being a workshop where you learn how to make the robot and also make it. (27th Jan : 3 to 5 PM ; 28th Jan : 2 to 5 PM)\\r\\nAnd the third day we will pit your robots against each other. (29th Jan : 3:30 to 5:30 PM)\"'),(901,76,673,'rules','[\"Two bots will face off each other at a time.\",\"Only bots made on the premises during the workshop would be allowed.\",\"Decision of the referee will be final.\",\"Arena dimensions and rules of gameplay will be given on the day itself.\"]'),(902,76,673,'start_time','\"2017-01-27 15:00\"'),(903,76,673,'end_time','\"2017-01-29 17:30\"'),(904,76,673,'venue','\"Pulsation Lab, Nilgiri\"'),(905,76,673,'contact_email','\"pulsation@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(906,77,676,'name','\"\\u2018LEGO\\u2019ing a Great Story\"'),(907,77,676,'description','\"An event for every Novel, Comic, Movie, TV show, Video Game fan. It has mystery, emotion, puzzle,  dialogue, painting, sound everything. So sharpen your story writing skills and be prepared to write an amazing story.\\r\\n \"'),(908,77,676,'rules','[\"There are 5 rounds. Each round deals with a particular aspect of a story. In each round, there is be a question which may have correct answer or have a subjective answer.\",\"1. Minimalist Poster\",\"2. Lateral Thinking Puzzle\",\"3. Fill Comic Book \",\"4. Tale of Painting\",\"5. Tale of Sound\",\"At final task is to combine answer of all these rounds and write one coherent story. Winner would be declared based on the final story which has unique use of elements of all five rounds.\"]'),(909,77,676,'contact_email','\"litcafe@felicity.iiit.ac.in\"'),(910,77,677,'tagline','\"What Constitutes a Great Story?\"'),(911,78,679,'name','\"Creator\\u2019s Dilemma : The Beginner\'s Guide \"'),(912,78,679,'tagline','\"Inside mind of a creater\"'),(913,78,679,'description','\"An interactive drama in form of a video game. A unique story about what goes through inside mind of a video game developer. \"'),(914,78,679,'rules','[\"The interactive drama is 2 hours long.\",\"At the end, participants will write their experience and their theory regarding mystery of the ending.\"]'),(915,79,681,'name','\"Treasure Hunt\"'),(916,79,681,'tagline','\"Treasure is out there!\"'),(917,79,681,'description','\"Mystery is all set waiting to be unfolded by Sherlock skills. Gather all your geeky friends, explore semi fictional world of IIIT in search of clues. \"'),(918,79,681,'rules','[\"The first three team to reach to the final treasure would be the winner.\"]'),(919,80,683,'name','\"Sherlock Screening and Quiz \"'),(920,80,683,'tagline','\"The Game is On\"'),(921,80,683,'description','\"Excited about Season 4 of BBC hit Sherlock? Well, join us in a mass vieiwing of the season finale where you dress up as your favourite character from Sherlock TV show! Oh, and there will be a trivia quiz with attractive prizes at the end! \"'),(922,81,685,'name','\" JAMin\' it out\"'),(923,81,685,'description','\"Long dragging speeches are not  your thing? Fret not, we got some of the best prompts from all over the internet and you got one minute to win. Join in the JAM with us and show us how wacky you can get! \"'),(924,82,687,'name','\"The Wire\"'),(925,82,687,'description','\"Three days of fest! A long time for several stories to unfold, events to happen but do you have it in your to best the best ofthe moments from the fest and present it to all. Extra points for satirical takes! Pre-registeration for this event is mandatory.\\r\\nThe best compliation wins super-amaing prizes.\\r\\n\"'),(926,83,689,'name','\" Freaky Friday\"'),(927,83,689,'description','\"Your favourite fictional character has swapped souls with you for a day. How will you get around your usual day now? Write us a crazy-awesome fanfiction and we\'ll reward you well!\\r\\n\"'),(928,84,691,'name','\"After Thought\"'),(929,84,691,'description','\"Is writing poetry is your passion or just a hobby? Send us your best poetic works recalling childhood memories and get a chance to have a oersonalised poetry guidance by a professional oh, and amazing prizes, of course.\\r\\n\\r\\n  \\r\\n\"'),(930,15,697,'description','\"The flagship event of Threads \\u0