e issues with registration or payment, contact us at <a href=\\\"mailto:webdev@felicity.iiit.ac.in\\\" class=\\\"underlined\\\">webdev@felicity.iiit.ac.in<\\/a>\"'),(1260,15,926,'button_link','\"auth\\/login\\/\"'),(1261,53,927,'description','\"Most famous and extensively played sports game on PC, FIFA 2015 is all set with a bang to steal every football freaks\' hearts. Skills matter, agreed. Agility and strategy matter, agreed. But what matters the most, is the spirit towards this sports. Be it a keyboard or a controller, when you are ready to become a Messi, the world won\'t stop you. \\r\\nSee you all at Zombie Zone, Felicity \'17.\\r\\nCheers! \"'),(1262,52,928,'description','\"\\\"Vroom!\\\". This sounds like Fast and this sounds like Furious. This sounds Fun isn\'t it??\\r\\nBeing on the Top isn\'t good enough. Maintaining it like a boss is what sounds like a TRUE Racer.\\r\\n\\r\\nZombie Zone,Felicity\'17 now has NFS Most Wanted in its store.\\r\\nNow have a Real Racing experience with your friends racing through \\r\\nthe streets of Rockport City and Brag about it coz U r the Boss.\\r\\nBeware of the Pursuit breakers though. One small mistake can be \\r\\na fatal error. Trust your instincts and the Force will be with you.\\r\\n\\r\\nSo get to the Garage and tune your car to rule the streets coz your \\r\\nCAR is your GOD.\"'),(1263,98,929,'description','\"Felicity Basketball League (FBL) is a 3 on 3 basketball event based on the format of NBA Jam. Come and show off your shooting, dribbling and passing skills and prove that you are the best ballers in town :D. \"'),(1264,93,930,'tagline','\"Dramebaaz Kahin Ka!\"'),(1265,91,931,'description','\"\'Knowledge is a never-ending ocean, and the more of the ocean we conquer, the more of the world we control.\'\\r\\n\\r\\nIIITH-MUN \'17 will be a memorable conference to participate in. We, the OC have taken considerable efforts to provide a platform for our delegates to grow in their understanding of world politics, h