ring and science. We expect to see some really innovative work. It will be conducted in 2 rounds, selected students in first will give their presentation in final round in Felicity 2017.\\r\\n\\r\\nJudging Criteria:\\r\\n\\r\\n- Correctness of facts\\r\\n- Methods of analysis\\r\\n- Innovativeness of idea\\r\\n- Presentation of solution or ideas\\r\\n- Practical feasibility or implication of ideas\"'),(1490,75,1094,'start_time','\"2017-01-16 08:00\"'),(1491,75,1094,'end_time','\"2017-01-16 23:45\"'),(1492,75,1095,'rules','[\"You will have twenty seconds to answer each question.\",\"There will be ten questions in each level before unlocking the next level.\",\"Time-based scoring.\",\"Multiple levels.\"]'),(1493,74,1096,'description','\"Quesions - https:\\/\\/docs.google.com\\/document\\/d\\/13zUa_FOmfCCIaSYr1Tt16uN7KCSN0LIEQRpdK5J6F78\\/edit?usp=sharing\\r\\n\\r\\nHas programming got you bored?\\r\\nNothing but text all over the screen?\\r\\nWell, not any more! Put your creative hats on and let\\u2019s get designing. We present to you - a blank canvas waiting to be filled, let your imagination run wild! There will be challenges where you would be required to design stunning visuals and simulations.\\r\\n\\r\\nRegistration link: <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/register\\/\\\" class=\\\"underlined\\\">https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/register\\/<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nThe link to the contest portal will be available at the time of the contest.\\r\\n\"'),(1494,74,1096,'status','\"The contest is live!\"'),(1495,74,1096,'button_link','\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/threads\\/visualizeit\\/submit\\/\"'),(1496,74,1096,'button_text','\"Click here to submit your answers\"'),(1497,74,1097,'description','\"Quesions - <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/docs.google.com\\/document\\/d\\/13zUa_FOmfCCIaSYr1Tt16uN7KCSN0LIEQRpdK5J6F78\\/edit?usp=sharing\\\">Link to questions<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nHas programming got you bored?\\r\\nNothing but text all over the screen?\\r\\nWell, not an