h your thoughts.\"'),(1511,84,1104,'status','\"live\"'),(1512,84,1105,'status','\"\"'),(1513,84,1106,'tagline','\"We write poem when we cease to be at peace with our thoughts.\"'),(1514,116,1107,'description','\"\\\"The man who does not read good books has no advantage over a man who can not read them\\\".  And here, the advantage, is the LitQuiz, of course! Battle your wits against the words well known in History, and rediscover lost tales and ballads of the past. Test your knowledge on everything Lit and take part in our pop-cult obsessed quiz! Winner takes it all! :) \"'),(1515,92,1108,'description','\"Virtual, Augmented & Mixed Reality are pipped to be the next big revolution\\r\\nafter PC Web & Mobile. They truly hold the potential to unlock and add\\r\\nlayers of immersive experience and create new solutions and products across\\r\\nuse cases in consumer sphere and enterprise. That said, the space is still\\r\\nin infancy and quite nebulous, evolving every day as it morphs and acquires\\r\\nnew form and functions.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhat is it like to be an entrepreneur in such an evolving space? How much\\r\\nof a foundation does one build on technology and solutions that are in\\r\\nflux? What are the fundamentals of entrepreneurship being applied and what\\r\\nis the level of agility maintained to succeed in this space?\\r\\n\\r\\nWe explore the VR AR MR spectrum from the prism of 4 different\\r\\nentrepreneurial perspectives, Technology, Art, Business & Community.\\r\\n\\r\\nJoin us for a special workshop curated and produced by vamrr\\u2122  (Virtual\\r\\nAugmented Mixed Reality & Visualization Ecosystem) and held at IIIT\\r\\nHyderabad, with the organizational support of E-Cell, IIIT Hyderabad as\\r\\npart of Felicity 2017\"'),(1516,92,1109,'status','\"Registrations are open!\"'),(1517,92,1109,'button_link','\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/talks-and-workshops\\/arvr\\/register\\/\"'),(1518,92,1109,'button_text','\"Click here to Register\"'),(1519,92,1109,'ve