ize education at your campus? Get your doubts cleared on your mobile device or Replace Xeroxed notes\\/assignments with digital copies are some of the things we can think of, let\\u2019s see what you can come up with?\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>Club & Event Management<\\/strong>: Be it club activities or large events like Felicity, chances of last-minute chaos are always high. What can you build to better plan, manage and execute so that this chaos is avoided?\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<li><strong>College Social<\\/strong>: College is where a person\\u2019s social life kick starts in full swing, no? Build mini-apps to enable that. Here are a few ideas from our side \\u2013 plan weekend trips or evening movies, keep track of items or money lent, make plans for someone\\u2019s birthday or just sit and gossip.\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<h2>Technical Documents<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p> Techincal introduction of Developing on Kaizala can be found <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/files\\/17\\/kaizala_intro.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">here<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<br>\\r\\nBy clicking to proceed for registration, you agree to the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/files\\/17\\/kaizala_tnc.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Use of Entries Agreement<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"submit\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" class=\\\"btn\\\">Submit<\\/a>\\r\\n\"'),(1669,126,1221,'rules','[\"This competition is open only to current students of an educational institute participating in Felicity 2017.\",\"Teams of maximum 3 members are allowed\",\"There will be 2 rounds: <li> Ideation \\u2013 Online, from 19 to 24 Jan 2017, and <\\/li><li>Development \\u2013 At IIITH campus, 10am \\u2013 6pm on Friday, 27 Jan 2017<\\/li>\",\"The winning team will receive a cash prize of INR 5000 per team member and the runners-up will receive a cash prize of INR 3000 per team member. Apart from this all teams selected for the Development round will receive Microsoft certificates. \",\"In the Ideation round teams 