l given according to first come first serve. So hurry up!<\\/u><\\/h3>\\r\\n<h3><u>Cost and Accommodation<\\/u><\\/h3>Registration fees is 1000 Rs. If you need accommodation in Hyderabad during workshop, we will provide it. You will need to pay for accommodation onsite. It will be based on per day basis.<br\\/>\\r\\n<h3><u>About workshop<\\/u><\\/h3>What we do on the Web changes every day. The web development industry is constantly evolving. While we may not be able to tell the day-to-day changes while they\\u2019re happening, it\'s easy for us to look back at the past few months and see that a lot of things we do now are much different than what we\'ve been doing before.\\r\\n\\r\\nBecause our work lies in one of the fastest-paced industries, it\'s important for us to predict and learn about what\'s coming up or risk being left in the web development dust.\\r\\n<h3><u>Here\\u2019s why you should join us<\\/u><\\/h3>Learn how to craft your ideas into something real! Coding is the ability to take the abstract and make it concrete. In this class we\\u2019ll show you how to go from no prior coding knowledge to crafting your own dynamic websites using HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Python and MYSQL.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>When<\\/strong>\\r\\nJanuary 27th-29th, 2017.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Where<\\/strong>\\r\\n[ Only Offline ]\\r\\nIIIT Hyderabad, Gachibowli, Hyderabad, Telangana, Pincode - 500032.\\r\\n<h3>Workshop Highlights<\\/h3><ul><li>Learn and interact with experts in the field of Web Development.\\r\\n<li>Practical demonstration for each and every module mentioned in course contents.\\r\\n<li>Improve your job prospects and get an edge over your counterparts.\\r\\n<li>Receive an unparalleled education on the art of computer security with personal one-to-one attention.\\r\\n<li>Covers all the basics for development of a server side website.\\r\\n<li>Get familiar with the latest tools and techniques required for rapid web development<\\/li>\\r\\n<!--<li>Hands on Demonstrations of