he Storm poster\\\" >\"'),(1787,116,1338,'rules','[\"Portal will be opened on event day.\"]'),(1788,101,1339,'description','\"Situation: Imagine yourself and a group of friends locked in a dimly lit room! The only key to break out of this place is hidden somewhere in that very room. Collect pieces of evidence and cooperate with your crew to solve this puzzle! Do you have what it takes or are you just gonna give up like the others? A unique event filled with rich lore of HBO latest drama Westworld.\\r\\nIf you have seen westworld, then you should be here.If you haven\\u2019t seen westworld, then you definitely should be here.\"'),(1789,116,1340,'start_time','\"2017-01-26 10:00\"'),(1790,116,1340,'end_time','\"\"'),(1791,76,1342,'start_time','\"2017-01-28 14:30\"'),(1792,76,1342,'end_time','\"2017-01-28 18:30\"'),(1793,76,1343,'description','\"Want to create the Messis and Ronaldos of the robotics world? This thrilling event is just for you. We will give you everything you need, and teach you everything you need to know. All you need to do is just come out and play!!\\r\\n\\r\\nThe first one hour will be a workshop where you make your own player.\\r\\nIn the second part which is open to all we will have a robo soccer tournament.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><u>About RoboSoccer<\\/h3><\\/u>\\r\\n\\r\\nIt is team game where you are hard wired along with your mates to your bots and the goal is to SCORE MORE GOALS than the opposition.\\r\\n\\r\\nThe bots are fine tuned and built as per requirement of number of forward, mid and defenders on the side. A bot is specially dedicated to serve as a GOALY!! \\r\\nChoose your style of bot and come down this Felicity to enjoy a one2one connect with your bot and celebrate team-spirit to win the ultimate Championship.\\r\\n\\r\\nHighlights\\r\\n\\r\\n1. Specialised bots\\r\\n2. Team game with tournament model\\r\\n3. Raspberry Pi up for grabs\\r\\n4. Free to add any functionality to the bots\\r\\n5. Enjoy the time with quality electronic football.