naware of them.\\r\\nAnything that moves, changes in time, has dynamics and in order that such dynamics function properly, it needs control. Control governs, or regulates, how the system behaves or functions. All electric\\/electronic appliances are controlled according to some control laws. They include the air-conditioners, refrigerators, TVs, radios, audio and video players, and of course, computers.\\r\\nControl is a fundamental discipline that underlies all our lives. The Out of Control Workshop aims at clarifying its far-reaching power, pursuing various new and exciting applications in the field of robotics , and exploring yet unknown new methodologies that contribute to the advancement of human lives.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><u>Workshop Highlights<\\/u><\\/h3>\\r\\n<li>Learn and interact with experts in the field of Robotics.<\\/li><li>Practical demonstration for each and every module mentioned in course contents.<\\/li><li>Improve your job prospects and get an edge over your counterparts.<\\/li><li>Receive an unparalleled education on control theory with personal one-to-one attention.<\\/li><li>Covers all the basics<\\/li><li>Get familiar with the latest tools and techniques used in controlling dynamic systems<\\/li>\\r\\n<h3><u>Workshop Details<\\/u><\\/h3>\\r\\n<li>All study material would be provided.<\\/li><li>All the necessary softwares would be provided<\\/li><li>You will need your laptop. So do try to get it ! Please inform us in advanceif you can\'t, we will arrange for you.<\\/li><li>Workshop will be of 3 hours.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Certificates from\\u00a0IIIT-Hyderabad\\u00a0will be provided to all the participants who complete the workshop<\\/li>\\r\\n<u><h3>Cost and Accommodation<\\/u><\\/h3>\\r\\nThis workshop is absolutely free ! if you need accommodation in Hyderabad during workshop, we will provide it. You will need to pay for accommodation on site. The charges will be per day basis. \\r\\n\"'),(1817,90,1365,'end_time','\"2017-01-27 13:00\"'),(1818,93,1366,'venue','\"Guest House Lawns\"'),(1819,128,1371,'name','\"EDM Night\"'),(1820,128,1371,'tagline','\" One&One and Paul Richard\"'),(1821,128,1371,'description','\"Experience the excitement of the world of electronic music as Felicity brings to you - EDM night!\\r\\nPaul Richard is finally making his way to India and the excitement in Hyderabad is going through the roof! Although he\\u2019s touring various cities in India, his gig at Felicity, IIIT Hyderabad is going to be bigger than anything you\\u2019ve ever seen. Travelling all the way from Italy, Paul surely knows how to get the crowd grooving with his music.\\r\\nOpening for him will be the iconic India duo One&One. One & One have played in an integral role in the growth of the electronic music scene in India. Having headlined at various Vh1 Supersonic nights, their sets are truly magical. Catch them live at Felicity, IIIT Hyderabad on 28th Jan.\\r\\nDon\'t miss out on this stellar night, \'nuff said.\"'),(1822,128,1371,'start_time','\"2017-01-28 19:00\"'),(1823,128,1371,'end_time','\"2017-01-28 23:00\"'),(1824,128,1371,'venue','\"Felicity Ground, IIIT Hyderabad\"'),(1825,129,1373,'name','\"Rahul Subramanian\"'),(1826,129,1373,'tagline','\"The Comedian\"'),(1827,129,1373,'description','\"So our Comedy night is here!\\r\\n\\r\\nHere we have performing for you a 29 year old married man from Bombay, who\\u2019s a struggling brand manager by the day and stand up comedian by the night ( and a disappointment to his father all day long ) . He graduated from IMT Ghaziabad,a feat by which he is still perplexed as to how did he manage it. \\r\\nAfter bringing disgrace to his father by failing to get into IIM , He decided he wasn\\u2019t done yet and decided to bring some more dishonor by becoming a stand up comedian.\\r\\n\\r\\nAnd boy,we are glad he did.\\r\\n\\r\\nPrepare to feel like having been injected with a bordering lethal dose of nitrous oxide, because we bring for you a gem of a comic that has been seen in all the big banners in India,and then some.\\r\\n\\r\\nSo without further ado we bring you one of the top comics of India! The Youtube star..\\r\\nRA-RA- RAHUL SUBRAMANIAN!\"'),(1828,129,1373,'start_time','\"2017-01-27 21:00\"'),(1829,129,1373,'end_time','\"2017-01-27 22:00\"'),(1830,129,1373,'venue','\"Felicity Ground, IIIT Hyderabad\"'),(1831,128,1374,'name','\"VH1 Supersonic Night\"'),(1832,128,1374,'tagline','\"One&One and Paul Richard\"'),(1833,128,1374,'og_image','\"felicity.iiith\\/photos\\/a.250886521665996.61489.135851036502879\\/1226052447482727\\/?type=3&theater\"'),(1834,128,1375,'og_image','\"\\/felicity.iiith\\/photos\\/a.250886521665996.61489.135851036502879\\/1226052447482727\\/?type=3&theater\"'),(1835,128,1376,'og_image','\"a.250886521665996.61489.135851036502879\\/1226052447482727\\/?type=3&theater\"'),(1836,128,1377,'og_image','\"\"'),(1837,130,1379,'name','\"DJ Workshop\"'),(1838,130,1379,'tagline','\" \"'),(1839,130,1379,'description','\"Ever wondered what DJ\'ing is all about?\\r\\n\\r\\nGet ready to make your friends groove and shake on your beats through the ultimate DJ workshop with in-house DJ\'s of the best clubs of the city.\\r\\nAnd the best part: it\'s completely free.\"'),(1840,130,1379,'start_time','\"2017-01-28 14:00\"'),(1841,130,1379,'end_time','\"2017-01-28 17:00\"'),(1842,130,1379,'venue','\"IIIT Hyderabad\"'),(1843,130,1380,'description','\"Ever wondered what DJ\'ing is all about?\\r\\n\\r\\nGet ready to make your friends groove and shake on your beats through the ultimate DJ workshop with in-house DJ\'s of the best clubs in the city.\\r\\nAnd the best part: it\'s completely free.\"'),(1844,124,1381,'end_time','\"2017-01-29 23:00\"'),(1845,98,1382,'description','\"Under the Hoop is a 3 on 3 basketball event based on the format of NBA Jam. Come and show off your shooting, dribbling and passing skills and prove that you are the best ballers in town ! \\r\\nRegister your team for FREE and stand a chance to win prizes worth up to 6K I