venative technique to unwind the mind at the end of the day, to let go of stresses and emotions, and simplify your life.<br>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Day 3 (29th Jan)<\\/h3>\\r\\n<h4>CONNECT. WITH YOUR INNER SELF<\\/h4>\\r\\nIn the third class, learn to connect with your inner self by listening to the heart\\u2019s voice. Observe your deepest feelings, make wise choices and weave your destiny<br>\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>When<\\/strong>\\r\\nJanuary 27th-29th, 10:00 am to 11:00 am 2017.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Where<\\/strong>\\r\\n[ Only Offline ]\\r\\nYoga Hall<br>\\r\\nIIIT Hyderabad, Gachibowli, Hyderabad, Telangana, Pincode - 500032.\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"www.heartfulness.org\\\">www.heartfulness.org<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/felicity.iiit.ac.in\\/files\\/17\\/heartfulness.jpg\\\" alt=\\\"Heartfulness poster\\\" \\/>\"'),(1917,135,1433,'venue','\"Yoga Hall, IIIT-Hyderabad\"'),(1918,135,1433,'contact_email','\"heartfulness.iiith@gmail.com\"'),(1919,135,1434,'start_time','\"2017-01-27 10:00\"'),(1920,135,1434,'end_time','\"2017-01-29 11:00\"'),(1921,135,1435,'description','\"<h3><u>About workshop<\\/u><\\/h3>\\r\\nIn a competitive world that recognizes and rewards external manifestation of success, <strong>\\u2018Heartfulness\\u2019<\\/strong> is a sure \\u2018game changer\\u2019 redefining success, rewards and joy.\\r\\n<br>\\r\\nThe workshop offers a simple and practical way to learn relaxation and heart-based meditation, which naturally blends in with the present day lives.\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><u>Why Heartfulness<\\/u><\\/h3>\\r\\nOur entire life is lead by feelings and inspirations, and that is the role of the Heart.\\r\\n<br>\\r\\nWith practice, \\u2018Heartfulness\\u2019 can initiate a series of transformation in a person, in terms of re-prioritizing objectives and targets. This transformation is towards creating harmony and excellence.\\u00a0\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Day 1 (27th Jan)<\\/h3>\\r\\n<strong>RELAX . MEDITATE : EXPAND CONCIOUSNESS<\\/strong>\\r\\nIn the first clas